        "created_at": "2025-07-31T16:36:18.112Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Currently Signal displays text on opposite sides for sender and receiver. I really don’t like this, especially when there are short messages.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/3/e/3e3b497a4daaee7b809deab521ef6f5476050c73.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/3e3b497a4daaee7b809deab521ef6f5476050c73\" title=\"Current Text Display\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/3/e/3e3b497a4daaee7b809deab521ef6f5476050c73.png\" alt=\"Current Text Display\" data-base62-sha1=\"8SwCKBAcu8QLUXIq0lsvpFLWLNp\" width=\"690\" height=\"342\" data-dominant-color=\"1B2233\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">Current Text Display</span><span class=\"informations\">1476×732 9.49 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>I would like to see an option to have it all moved to one side, along with that an option that allows the text to not be limited by a certain width (to allow full width of the window to be used).</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/4/5/4593f95cb85178fb043543c00d441423fb87c2b7.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/4593f95cb85178fb043543c00d441423fb87c2b7\" title=\"One Side Text\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/4/5/4593f95cb85178fb043543c00d441423fb87c2b7.png\" alt=\"One Side Text\" data-base62-sha1=\"9VvYF95HPuQqSfvcU7HK5lfSbMb\" width=\"690\" height=\"342\" data-dominant-color=\"1B2233\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">One Side Text</span><span class=\"informations\">1476×732 9.47 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>I included two example images for the ease of sharing what I mean since I could not be more descriptive with it.</p>",
